descriptionHtml:
This is my custon ENB config of Boris Vorontsov\'s ENB Series version 0.102

I tried to achieve a realistic look, at least for me.

This version is without SSAO. If you want to use it open the enbseries.ini and go to the [EFFECTS] section and change EnableAmbientOcclusion=False to EnableAmbientOcclusion=True.
bFloatPointRenderTarget in your SkyrimPrefs.ini must be set to 1 also.

Known issues:

- glowing water foam at night (not fixable for now)
- weird looking water lods (not fixable for now)
author: Tywele
